{"tid":100043,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖]最差賀年禮物","createTime":"2017-01-29T16:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T08:35:21.000Z","uid":13610,"like":20,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"00bfd61efe6cc01685fe56c4f8146aedc5a2ac63","tid":100043,"uid":13610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:16:38.000Z","msg":"每次拜年，親朋戚友緊會帶份禮物上樓以示心意。我爸個邊有好多兄弟姊妹，咁所以收到嘅禮物都會有好多，但有啲親戚緊係會送啲垃圾過嚟。廢話少講，去圖。<br />\n<br />\n首先，有新年炸彈 - 嘉頓高級雜餅<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/29/233437_b78044bd2c3c15cc8c1259aa0eb82a71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F29%2F233437_b78044bd2c3c15cc8c1259aa0eb82a71.jpg&h=7682dfca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/29/233529_69170467a314ae03d48bfbc0cde09cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F29%2F233529_69170467a314ae03d48bfbc0cde09cd9.jpg&h=d4e9ace0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實我覺得嘉頓餅都唔差，中間朱古力嗰隻，威化餅都會食下，而且起碼肚餓嘅時候頂到下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最難頂，其實係雜乜牌朱古力<br />\n<br />\n雜乜牌1號<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dVb3i9y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdVb3i9y.jpg&h=003e5044&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雜乜牌2號 (冇拆曬，一見到又係呢啲雜乜朱古力，即刻停手，包返好佢回贈比啲好親戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/29/235338_1f260dd54140ba023d12dde52600e700.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F29%2F235338_1f260dd54140ba023d12dde52600e700.jpg&h=dc2ee7d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雜乜牌3號(個人認為最極品)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/29/234443_1161f19772aa190588564959da1b4e2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F29%2F234443_1161f19772aa190588564959da1b4e2d.jpg&h=df48ea30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到啲各種唔同口味嘅朱古力已經想嘔<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/29/234509_d64c48e676f52262575e7f3dbf5f77a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F29%2F234509_d64c48e676f52262575e7f3dbf5f77a4.jpg&h=898bd4fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n爸媽年紀都有返咁上下，而且我又唔係小朋友，點解硬係鐘意買啲朱古力送比人？大佬呀，你都有返咁上下年紀，愛錫身體嘅都唔會食咁多呢啲甜食啦。<br />\n<br />\n都算啦，仲要啲味奇奇怪怪，咩orange呀，raspberry呀嗰啲，搵鬼食咩(如果個啲係名牌朱古力嘅話，對唔住，小女子孤陋寡聞，唔識欣)。細個已經伏過，滿心歡喜食左粒士多啤梨同橙味朱古力。嘩，真係難食到講粗口。你話金莎、麥提沙個啲正常口味嘅都話易入口姐，真係唔知啲親戚咩心態。<br />\n<br />\n不過唔緊要，你地咁鐘意食朱古力，就送返比你地啦，我諗你啲仔女都會鐘意食嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n另外都要表揚一下好親戚<br />\n1.<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/30/001038_b95ae03d19e89ff524185890c993221a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F30%2F001038_b95ae03d19e89ff524185890c993221a.jpg&h=c2be067b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2.<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/30/001053_aaf901b7fdd0510e93487ed7b941c8e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F30%2F001053_aaf901b7fdd0510e93487ed7b941c8e6.jpg&h=9278741c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有啲，唔影啦<br />\n<br />\n希望大家將心比己，買禮物比人之前用個腦諗下，正所謂<br />\n己所不欲 勿施於人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝大家收到正常嘅禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efbd06e1d235182550016238c8eb19e0e995c9dc","tid":100043,"uid":13610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:19:39.000Z","msg":"p.s. 屋企人年年買正常野如壽桃牌鮑魚麵，冇伏過人，除左送朱古力比我地嗰啲 我地會轉贈返啲朱古力比佢"},{"pid":"86cfb8cfc9d4152296b08ed7fb43214639e8641d","tid":100043,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:22:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>p.s. 屋企人年年買正常野如<span style=\"color: red;\">壽桃牌鮑魚麵</span>，冇伏過人，除左送朱古力比我地嗰啲 我地會轉贈返啲朱古力比佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最憎收到呢盒野"},{"pid":"f3b3744cf82a3b71bdd44393d77b9b70090b190a","tid":100043,"uid":17427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:25:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>p.s. 屋企人年年買正常野如<span style=\"color: red;\">壽桃牌鮑魚麵</span>，冇伏過人，除左送朱古力比我地嗰啲 我地會轉贈返啲朱古力比佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最憎收到呢盒野</blockquote><br />\n好食喎呢隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2765dcc02b1fd6f834986bba1838cfd1d8a629c4","tid":100043,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:27:06.000Z","msg":"壽桃牌鮑魚麵<br />\n落一棵生菜加醬撈黎食一絕<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9158e40f7de290bda495bedc7ebf947239b9d0b1","tid":100043,"uid":28523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:29:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>p.s. 屋企人年年買正常野如<span style=\"color: red;\">壽桃牌鮑魚麵</span>，冇伏過人，除左送朱古力比我地嗰啲 我地會轉贈返啲朱古力比佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最憎收到呢盒野</blockquote><br />\n好食喎呢隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好重味精<br />\n個人推薦 三潤蝦子麵 要段斤計個種先made in hk 用盒係made in china"},{"pid":"d82d8b5c2a0532a627f79045c2ed03733b8ef421","tid":100043,"uid":13610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:35:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最憎收到呢盒野</blockquote><br />\n好食喎呢隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好重味精<br />\n個人推薦 三潤蝦子麵 要段斤計個種先made in hk 用盒係made in china</blockquote><br />\n等我話比屋企人知先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 壽桃鮑魚麵係鹹左啲，我會落少啲醬食/加啲水"},{"pid":"3ddfe9377b6e4e17a82a127746fd6a90813db69f","tid":100043,"uid":10531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T17:53:00.000Z","msg":"今日有親戚收到雙黃白蓮蓉月餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1107fbe2ebc39cb638e95527224f01df661d6451","tid":100043,"uid":54875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T17:59:49.000Z","msg":"鮑魚麵起碼真係肚餓唔想落街可以煮嚟食<br />\n果啲垃圾朱古力見到狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab39ee4639d523837e440a16487e57da3534364","tid":100043,"uid":14016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T18:01:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日有親戚收到雙黃白蓮蓉月餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑左出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab9c33fec8e406bd94ef352b12627fbbce77b359","tid":100043,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T18:04:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>今日有親戚收到雙黃白蓮蓉月餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑左出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔送冰皮比你咪偷笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c19ebbd713ae9cb201254593baab1f9ae3728aa","tid":100043,"uid":17427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T18:10:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日有親戚收到雙黃白蓮蓉月餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\