/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />究竟要幾無恥先送得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢隻野又好味 成本又唔全同金莎唔差得幾多<br />\n你就覺得要份禮個標價貴一貴先顯得出自己貴格<br />\n呢d咪節日商品化影響囇咩都用錢去衡量<br />\n仲有係中國人先咁介意面子<br />\n送份禮都介意體面排場<br />\n咁怕蝕底你咪唔好送囉"},{"pid":"3c3ccc4e4ac151caf3c2dbe91baab98c80afd562","tid":100043,"uid":4058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:48:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我有個親戚年年都買樂家杏仁糖比我呀爺呀嫲但係唔諗下佢地七老八十點咬到粒硬到乜既糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食到排牙甩曬都應該食唔到一粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c640577e3fcf9b3717b67ec1723f1237e117d4","tid":100043,"uid":55868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:48:31.000Z","msg":"你平時點對人， 人地咪點對你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bca252edc2795401290acc890ff921575051bc8","tid":100043,"uid":13610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:22:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雜乜牌一號係惠康$100/4盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8bcaaf4b5e8d08fae42dbb48318532a72f013d1","tid":100043,"uid":78889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:32:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n呢隻好食喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好食還好食,但咁cheap雞送出去都嫌侮辱自己人格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\